{"tid":2398234,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張展綁輪椅上庭 母：她很瘦滿面皺紋","createTime":"2021-02-07T06:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T15:40:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ccde4d4a93ab43b75ff51b4bb46270da8f86f1","tid":2398234,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210207/IUEGIA2A2JB4XCUM7TXK6YFJWY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210207%2FIUEGIA2A2JB4XCUM7TXK6YFJWY%2F&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=6fdfa287\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210207%2FIUEGIA2A2JB4XCUM7TXK6YFJWY%2F&h=7d1542bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210207/IUEGIA2A2JB4XCUM7TXK6YFJWY/</a><br />\n<br />\n張展綁輪椅上庭 母：她很瘦滿面皺紋<br />\n<br />\n去年曾到武漢拍攝封城情況的內地公民記者張展，被當局以尋釁滋事罪重囚4年。旅居英國的維權人士王劍虹，昨首度公開張去年底於上海浦東新區法院出庭受審的照片，相中可見絕食多時的張骨瘦如柴，戴上手銬坐上輪椅，腰間被纒一道寬帶，就像被綁進法庭。據悉，早前張仍在半絕食狀態，當局並以疫情為由不准張母探監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共藉疫情阻張母探監<br />\n<br />\n王劍虹在Twitter留言指，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張展在去年5月被捕，此後曾絕食抗議半年，當日庭審僅兩個多小時就完結，她在庭上說：「這是審判你的法庭，不是審判我的法庭。」張母在庭審後接受香港有線電視訪問時說：「推（輪椅）過來的時候我能看見她的臉，很瘦很瘦，滿面皺紋，我從背影看見她的腿很細很細的。」<br />\n<br />\n張母又形容她身體狀況很差，說話也沒有力氣。早前有消息指出，張展因為「不想在封閉的邏輯圈打轉」，表明不會就當局判刑上訴。<br />\n<br />\n張展被判刑後，加拿大全球事務部與美國、英國、德國等14個媒體自由聯盟國家發聯合聲明，批評北京打壓新聞自由，並關注張展被拘捕及受到不公平審判，敦促中方立刻釋放張展和其他因報道疫情而被拘留的人士。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/ Twitter<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/C5KcxcYsVRUgjUZvRSgykH2DmwE=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NR2QRZH2BRCRDEB327FTK5MIDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FC5KcxcYsVRUgjUZvRSgykH2DmwE%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNR2QRZH2BRCRDEB327FTK5MIDQ.jpg&h=11618c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■張展（中）上庭的照片首度曝光，明顯消瘦不少。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OBUQCL5gZMcoGjyqJf71VIFdNbs=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UAZ23JZD2ZDSHGVQRHHYSP6BRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOBUQCL5gZMcoGjyqJf71VIFdNbs%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUAZ23JZD2ZDSHGVQRHHYSP6BRU.jpg&h=988d917e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張展"},{"pid":"c29618ecdfd9ee5127ec0240aa347063ad7d8a4a","tid":2398234,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35631112fed83bad68ba83fefe82db07f98fb0e","tid":2398234,"uid":208553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f5ad7bf00ebbc8e60d4416dd39073d6e202c4bc","tid":2398234,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"想像唔到佢遭受左乜"},{"pid":"18287929ffbca9f32b8d0fe82671f75771db3375","tid":2398234,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2b69f998e7c2d1e53ba9f027f6359cb8c271fd","tid":2398234,"uid":46161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6de02445437b6ea742c5522006ede80c060bc0","tid":2398234,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"